	Ancient Poison
		Power, 1 Energy:
		Artifacts do no longer negate Poison this combat. Apply 4 Poison to ALL enemies.

	
Character-specific relics
	Byrd carpet
		Boss relic: 
		Replaces Flying carpet. Start each combat with 3 Flight. If you have 1 or 2 Flight at the start of your turn, set it to 3 again.
	Cooking Book
		Common relic: 
		Start each combat with 1 Brewing.
	Ancient Magnet
		Uncommon relic: 
		Enemies have 1 less Strength per Artifact on them. You may use Artifact potions on enemies.

Other relics
	Red Beast Statue
		Uncommon relic:
		Potion rewards are ?% more likely to be rare potions.
	Blowpipe
		Rare relic: 
		Potions you throw affect ALL enemies.
